{# Image Generation Section #}
<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="image-generation">Image generation</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Images are generated to match the council's theme and region. The system creates:
</p>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
    <div class="ndx-image-type-card">
      <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Hero Images</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body-s">
        Large banner images for section landing pages, showing landscapes and townscapes matching the council's character.
      </p>
      <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--blue">~25 images</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
    <div class="ndx-image-type-card">
      <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Councillor Headshots</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body-s">
        Professional headshots representing diverse council members typical of UK local government.
      </p>
      <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--green">~8 images</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
    <div class="ndx-image-type-card">
      <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Location Photos</h3>
      <p class="govuk-body-s">
        Photos of buildings, facilities, and local landmarks for directory entries and service pages.
      </p>
      <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--yellow">~12 images</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Theme matching</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Image prompts incorporate the council's theme and region:
