<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li><strong>Coastal councils</strong> - harbour views, beach scenes, fishing boats, sea views</li>
  <li><strong>Industrial heritage</strong> - converted mills, former colliery sites, brick architecture</li>
  <li><strong>Market towns</strong> - high streets, market squares, stone buildings, countryside</li>
  <li><strong>University towns</strong> - historic buildings, student areas, cultural venues</li>
</ul>

